THE ATLANTA FIELD OFFICE
IS ASKING FOR OUR HELP

02:16.870 --> 02:20.397
IN A STRING OF MURDERS
THEY'VE CONNECTED
ON THE HSK DATABASE.

02:20.440 --> 02:22.408
LAST NIGHT THE BODY
OF A JOHN DOE WAS FOUND

02:22.440 --> 02:24.601
IN A TRUCK STOP REST ROOM
IN CHA'ITANOOGA, TENNESSEE.

02:24.640 --> 02:28.906
AND THE DAY BEFORE,
THE BODY OF 61-YEAR-OLD
CLAIRE WESTCHESTER

02:28.940 --> 02:34.173
WAS DISCOVERED IN
A BIRMINGHAM, ALABAMA,
TRUCK STOP REST ROOM.

02:34.220 --> 02:35.744
THEY HAD BOTH BEEN...

02:35.780 --> 02:37.418
IT'S ON YOUR TABLETS.

02:37.450 --> 02:39.281
THEY'D BEEN STABBED
MULTIPLES TIMES,

02:39.320 --> 02:41.288
AND THEY'D BOTH BEEN
POSED POSTMORTEM.

02:41.320 --> 02:43.254
WELL, HE DEMEANS
HIS VICTIMS,
THAT'S FOR SURE.

02:43.290 --> 02:45.429
THEY'RE BOUND TO
A URINAL WITH ROPE.

02:45.460 --> 02:47.291
Rossi: HE LEFI' ONE HELL OF
A CALLING CARD.

02:47.330 --> 02:49.525
WELL, THE LACK OF BLOOD
SUGGESTS THAT THEY
WERE KILLED SOMEWHERE ELSE

02:49.570 --> 02:50.423
AND THEN DISPOSED OF HERE.

02:50.470 --> 02:52.563
