ARE BOTH SHALLOW AND DEEP.

02:52.600 --> 02:54.329
IT COULD BE SOME SORT
OF SYSTEMATIC TORTURE.

02:54.370 --> 02:56.736
Lewis: WELL,
THERE ARE NO OBVIOUS
SIGNS OF SEXUAL ASSAULT.

02:56.770 --> 02:59.739
