03:07.620 --> 03:09.349
HE PROBABLY THOUGHT
BY CROSSING STATE LINES

03:09.390 --> 03:11.540
HE'D PREVENT THE AUTHORITIES
FROM CONNECTING THE TWO MURDERS.

03:11.590 --> 03:12.579
