TO STATE THE OBVIOUS,

03:12.620 --> 03:14.417
BUT WE'RE MOST LIKELY
LOOKING FOR A TRUCK DRIVER.

03:14.460 --> 03:16.621
ATLANTA IS ONE OF THE
COUNTRY'S TOP LONG-HAUL HUBS.

03:16.660 --> 03:19.697
IT'S ONE OF THE FEW
CITIES IN AMERICA SERVICED
BY 3 MAJOR INTERSTATES.

03:19.730 --> 03:22.563
THERE ARE HUNDREDS
OF OPEN CASES
ON THE HSK DATABASE,

03:22.600 --> 03:25.797
AND FINDING THIS UNSUB
IS GOING TO BE LIKE FINDING
A NEEDLE IN A HAYSTACK.

03:25.830 --> 03:27.331
WITH THE ABILITY TO MOVE
AROUND THE NATION,

03:27.370 --> 03:29.304
THERE'S NOTHING TO SUGGEST
HE'LL STOP ANYTIME SOON.

03:29.340 --> 03:30.898
WHEELS UP IN 30.

03:47.290 --> 03:49.588
