FORGIVENESS."

05:33.560 --> 05:34.652
HONORE DE BALZAC.

05:34.700 --> 05:37.828
IN A 2009 REPORT,
IT WAS SUSPECT ED
THAT SERIAL KILLERS

05:37.870 --> 05:39.633
OPERATING AS LONG-HAUL
TRUCK DRIVERS

05:39.670 --> 05:42.730
ARE RESPONSIBLE FOR
CLOSE TO 500 MURDERS
OVER THE LAST 3 DECADES.

05:42.770 --> 05:44.362
AND THAT NUMBER
HASN'T GONE DOWN.

05:44.410 --> 05:45.900
SO WHAT ELSE DO WE KNOW
ABOUT TRUCKERS?

05:45.940 --> 05:48.875
WELL, MOST SEE
LONG-HAULING AS
A LIFESTYLE, NOT A JOB.

05:48.910 --> 05:50.707
LIVING A LIFE
OF SOLITUDE
ON THE OPEN ROAD.

05:50.750 --> 05:52.877
WELL, OFTENTIMES THAT
COMES WITH A TREMENDOUS
AMOUNT OF STRESS,

05:52.920 --> 05:54.842
HAVING TO MEET
SCHEDULED DEADLINES
FOR MONTHS AT A TIME.

05:54.880 --> 05:56.541
AND WITH THE RIGHT
KIND OF PRESSURE,

05:56.590 --> 05:57.887
THE UNSUB
COULD HAVE SNAPPED.

05:57.920 --> 05:59.615
VICTIMOLOGY
SPEAKS TO THAT.

05:59.660 --> 06:01.912
BOTH VICTIMS WERE RANDOM,
JOHN DOE APPEARED
TO BE HOMELESS,

06:01.960 --> 06:04.986
AND CLAIRE WESTCHESTER
WAS THE COMPLETE OPPOSITE.

06:05.030 --> 06:07.749
YEAH, LOOKS LIKE SHE LIVED
IN COLLEGE PARK FOR
THE LAST 20 YEARS.

06:07.800 --> 06:09.893
SHE'D BEEN HAPPILY MARRIED
TO HER HIGH SCHOOL SWEETHEART

06:09.930 --> 06:12.125
AND TAUGHT AT
THE LOCAL ELEMENTARY SCHOOL.

06:12.170 --> 06:15.560
IT DOESN'T MAKE ANY SENSE.
WHY GO FROM LOW-
TO HIGH-RISK VICTIMS?

06:15.600 --> 06:17.602
YEAH, THESE TYPES
OF UNSUBS TYPICALLY
TARGET VICTIMS

06:17.640 --> 06:19.505
LIKE RU NAWAYS,
TRANSIENTS,
AND PROSTITUTES.

06:19.540 --> 06:21.872
SO APART FROM EACH OF THEM
BEING IN THEIR EARLY 60$,

06:21.910 --> 06:23.138
THERE'S NO CONNECTION
BETWEEN THE TWO?

06:23.180 --> 06:25.398
MAYBE AGE IS THE CONNECTION.
HE COULD BE CHOOSING

06:25.450 --> 06:26.917
HIS VICTIMS BECAUSE
THEY'RE EASIER TARGETS.

06:26.950 --> 06:28.508
OR THEY COULD BE SURROGATES.

06:28.550 --> 06:30.040
