HE CUTS OFF THE EARS.

06:30.090 --> 06:31.614
HE'S FELT IGNORED
ALL HIS LIFE.

06:31.650 --> 06:33.459
THE VICTIMS REPRESENT
SOME TYPE OF AUTHORITY FIGURE.

06:33.490 --> 06:36.084
THAT WOULD EXPLAIN
WHY CLAIRE WESTCHESTER
WAS TARGETED.

06:36.120 --> 06:37.724
SHE WAS A SCHOOLTEACHER.

06:37.760 --> 06:39.990
WHAT ABOUT
A PARENTAL FIGURE?

06:40.030 --> 06:41.122
IT'S POSSIBLE HE CHOSE
AND OLDER MALE

06:41.160 --> 06:42.923
AND OLDER FEMALE VICTIM
FOR A REASON.

06:42.970 --> 06:45.097
ALL RIGHT, WHEN WE LAND,
MORGAN, YOU AND REID
GO TO THE M.E.

06:45.130 --> 06:46.836
DAVE AND JJ,
GO ON TO CHATTANOOGA,

06:46.870 --> 06:48.929
