07:54.840 --> 07:56.660
I TRIED HER CELL.

07:56.710 --> 07:57.802
NO ANSWER.

07:57.840 --> 08:00.877
I CALLED THE SCHOOL.

08:00.910 --> 08:04.903
THEY SAID SHE'D
BEEN GONE FOR HOURS.

08:04.950 --> 08:08.818
MR. WESTCHESTER,
CAN YOU THINK OF ANYONE

08:08.850 --> 08:10.681
WHO WOULD WANT
TO HARM YOUR WIFE?

08:10.720 --> 08:14.087
NO. EVERYBODY LOVED HER.

08:14.120 --> 08:15.917
ESPECIALLY THE KIDS.

08:15.960 --> 08:19.054
I UNDERSTAND THAT
SHE WAS A TEACHER
FOR QUITE SOME TIME.

08:19.090 --> 08:20.796
WE COULDN'T HAVE
ANY KIDS OF OUR OWN,

08:20.830 --> 08:23.924
