08:23.970 --> 08:25.858
SHE SOUNDS LIKE
A WONDERFUL PERSON.

08:25.900 --> 08:27.891
THE HOLIDAYS
WERE HER FAVORITE.

08:27.940 --> 08:29.703
SHE WOULD MAKE SURE
THAT EVERY KID

08:29.740 --> 08:32.607
HAD AT LEAST ONE PRESENT
TO OPEN ON CHRISTMAS MORNING.

08:32.640 --> 08:36.178
