OR AROUND THE DISPOSAL SITES.

08:44.950 --> 08:47.589
I CROSSED AND THEN
CRISS-CROSSED THEM
WITH THE 3 INTERSTATES,

08:47.620 --> 08:48.985
BUT NONE OF THEM FIT
THE TIMELINE.

08:49.020 --> 08:50.829
EXPAND YOUR LIST TO INCLUDE
FREELANCE TRUCKERS

08:50.860 --> 08:52.919
AND CHECK THAT AGAINST
WEIGH STATIONS
ALONG THE ROUTE.

08:52.960 --> 08:53.927
I'LL HIT YOU BACK
WHEN I HAVE SOMETHING.

08:53.960 --> 08:55.848
WHAT ARE YOU THINKING?

08:55.900 --> 08:57.868
HOW MANY TRUCK STOPS
ARE THERE

08:57.900 --> 09:00.164
BETWEEN ATLANTA
AND THE DISPOSAL SITES?

