OR CLOSED FOR RENOVATIONS.

09:07.210 --> 09:08.336
WHY?

09:08.380 --> 09:10.348
BECAUSE THE UNSUB
PASSED UP SECLUDED AREAS

09:10.380 --> 09:12.610
