DELAYED THE DISCOVERY
OF THE BODIES.

09:12.650 --> 09:14.311
INSTEAD, HE DID THE OPPOSITE.

09:14.350 --> 09:16.170
HE LEFT THEM
IN PUBLIC PLACES.

09:16.220 --> 09:18.313
IT DOESN'T MAKE ANY SENSE.
WHY WOULD HE DO THAT?

09:18.350 --> 09:20.716
BECAUSE TRUCK STOPS
AREN'T DISPOSAL SITES,

09:20.760 --> 09:22.819
THEY MEAN SOMETHING TO HIM.

09:25.030 --> 09:27.089
[CAMERA CLICKING]

09:28.630 --> 09:32.191
THE MANAGER SAID
THE BUSIEST HOURS
FOR THIS STOP

09:32.230 --> 09:33.197
ARE BETWEEN 5:00 AND 6 AM.

09:33.240 --> 09:35.891
ACCORDING TO THE REPORT,
THE BODY WAS DISCOVERED

09:35.940 --> 09:38.101
BY A TRUCKER AROUND 3 AM.

09:38.140 --> 09:40.734
SO THIS GUY KNEW THE PATTERN.

09:40.780 --> 09:42.941
WELL, THE EXTERIOR LOCK
WAS BUSTED.

09:42.980 --> 09:46.143
HE DIDN'T SEEM TOO CONCERNED
ABOUT BEING INTERRUPTED.

09:46.180 --> 09:47.772
ALL RIGHT,
WELL, LET'S PLAY THIS OUT.

09:47.820 --> 09:49.742
WE KNOW THIS ISN'T FAR
FROM THE LONG-HAUL HUB.

09:49.790 --> 09:52.111
MAYBE THE UNSUB'S
FAMILIAR WITH THE AREA.

09:52.150 --> 09:55.608
LIKELY HIS ROUTE EITHER
ORIGINATED OR ENDED IN ATLANTA,

09:55.660 --> 09:58.128
WHICH IS ROUGHLY
A 2 1/2 HOUR DRIVE FROM HERE.

09:58.160 --> 10:00.094
SO BEING A TRUCKER,
HE'S USED TO BEING
ON THE ROAD

10:00.130 --> 10:01.688
FOR LONG PERIODS
OF TIME.

10:01.730 --> 10:03.994
EXACTLY. SO 2 1/2 HOURS
INTO HIS ROUTE,

10:04.030 --> 10:06.066
HE'S NOT GONNA STOP
AND TAKE A BREAK.

10:06.100 --> 10:08.830
RIGHT. TRUCKER'S MENTALITY--
GET TO WHERE YOU NEED TO GO.

10:08.870 --> 10:10.906
THAT COULD BE HOW
HE KNEW THE TRAFFIC FLOW.

10:10.940 --> 10:13.829
HE KNEW THAT MOST TRUCKERS
HEADING IN AND OUT OF ATLANTA

10:13.880 --> 10:16.132
WOULD JUST SKIP OVER
THIS STOP.

10:16.180 --> 10:20.139
IT'S STILL HIGH-RISK,
CONSIDERING HE'S STAGING
A BODY IN A PUBLIC PLACE.

10:20.180 --> 10:22.045
HIS COMPULSION
OUTWEIGHS THE RISK.

10:22.080 --> 10:23.980
MAYBE THE THRILL
IS WHAT GETS HIM OFF.

10:24.020 --> 10:25.681
I MEAN, HE HAD
TO HAVE KNOWN THE BODY
WOULD BE DISCOVERED

10:25.720 --> 10:27.358
SOONER
RATHER THAN LATER.

10:27.390 --> 10:30.029
PULLING OFF SOMETHING
THIS CALCULATED
AND ELABORATE

10:30.060 --> 10:32.085
SPEAKS TO HIS LEVEL
OF EXPERIENCE.

10:32.130 --> 10:33.859
[SIGHS]

10:33.900 --> 10:36.152
WHICH MEANS THERE'S
A STRONG POSSIBILITY

10:36.200 --> 10:39.692
HE'S BEEN KILLING A LOT
LONGER THAN WE THOUGHT.

10:40.900 --> 10:43.164
YOUR MOVE.

10:43.210 --> 10:46.202
COME ON, SLOWPOKE.

10:47.910 --> 10:49.002
I WIN.

10:49.040 --> 10:50.041
HA HA!

10:50.080 --> 10:52.241
WAIT, HOW'D YOU DO THAT?

10:52.280 --> 10:54.271
ALL RIGHT, BEST OF 5.

10:56.450 --> 10:59.089
OK, SPILL IT.

10:59.120 --> 11:01.088
HOW LONG ARE YOU GONNA
KEEP ME IN SUSPENSE?

11:01.120 --> 11:03.429
DID YOU POP THE QUESTION?

11:03.460 --> 11:06.088
SHE SAID YES.

11:06.130 --> 11:09.224
LUCKY GIRL.

11:10.170 --> 11:12.388
LISTEN, THERE'S, UH,

11:12.430 --> 11:16.389
THERE'S SOMETHING I WANTED
TO TALK TO YOU ABOUT.

11:16.440 --> 11:20.228
YOU AND I, WE'VE BEEN
GETTING TO KNOW
ONE ANOTHER RECENTLY,

11:20.280 --> 11:23.101
AND THAT'S BEEN WONDERFUL.

11:23.150 --> 11:24.708
NOW WITH THE WEDDING
COMING UP,

11:24.750 --> 11:28.846
I...I WAS HOPING
THAT MY ENTIRE FAMILY

11:28.880 --> 11:32.008
COULD BE THERE.

11:32.050 --> 11:34.257
INCLUDING MY BIOLOGICAL
FATHER.

11:34.290 --> 11:36.178
I WAS JUST THINKING MAYBE
I COULD REACH OUT TO HIM--

11:36.220 --> 11:38.484
NO. ABSOLUTELY NOT.

11:38.530 --> 11:40.088
WHY?

11:40.130 --> 11:43.019
THAT MAN IS THE REASON
YOU WERE TAKEN FROM ME.

11:43.070 --> 11:47.393
YOUR FATHER AND I HAD
A COMPLICATED RELATIONSHIP.

11:47.440 --> 11:50.102
I HAVEN'T SPOKEN TO HIM
IN YEARS,

11:50.140 --> 11:52.700
AND GOD ONLY KNOWS
WHERE HE IS.

11:55.940 --> 11:58.249
I DIDN'T MEAN
TO UPSET YOU, MOTHER.

11:58.280 --> 12:00.840
I'M SORRY.

12:00.880 --> 12:02.177
IT'S JUST TOO PAINFUL.

12:02.220 --> 12:06.316
LET'S KEEP THE PAST
IN THE PAST. HMM?

12:07.420 --> 12:08.387
[EXHALES]

12:08.420 --> 12:11.218
ALL RIGHT, YOUR TURN.

12:11.260 --> 12:14.024
FINALLY GOT AN I.D.
ON JOHN DOE.

12:14.060 --> 12:16.927
FRANK MYERS OF ATLANTA.
WE WERE ABLE TO I.D. HIM
THROUGH HIS DENTAL RECORDS.

12:16.970 --> 12:18.426
LOOKS LIKE HE'S BEEN
IN AND OUT OF HOMELESS SHELTERS

12:18.470 --> 12:20.392
FOR THE PAST COUPLE OF YEARS.

12:20.440 --> 12:22.863
FOR SOMEONE ON THE STREETS,
I'D SAY HE HAS SOME PRETTY
EXPENSIVE DENTAL WORK.

12:22.910 --> 12:25.367
AND THEY'RE STILL
TRYING TO LOCATE
HIS NEXT OF KIN.

12:25.410 --> 12:26.206
