RULED A C.O.D.?

12:26.240 --> 12:27.935
EXSANGUINATION
FROM PENETRATING WOUNDS.

12:27.980 --> 12:30.107
IN BOTH CASES, THE KILLER
SEVERED MAJOR ARTERIES.

12:30.150 --> 12:32.072
WERE YOU ABLE TO DETERMINE
WHEN THE EAR WAS REMOVED?

12:32.110 --> 12:33.543
POSTMORTEM.

12:33.580 --> 12:34.649
I ALSO FOUND THIS.

12:34.680 --> 12:37.808
BURLAP FIBERS EMBEDDED
IN BOTH VICTIMS'
WOUND TRACKS.

12:37.850 --> 12:40.978
HE STABS THEM THROUGH A BAG.
THAT'S UNUSUAL BEHAVIOR
FOR A SADIST.

12:41.020 --> 12:43.955
THEY GET OFF ON WATCHING
THEIR VICTIMS
AS THEY INFLICT PAIN.

12:43.990 --> 12:46.322
WELL, IT APPEARS THE KILLER
TRIED NUMEROUS TIMES TO STAB

12:46.360 --> 12:48.828
BUT HIT THE BONE,
BEFORE HE GOT IT RIGHT.

12:48.860 --> 12:51.829
WELL, THIS MIGHT NOT
BE OVERKILL LIKE
WE INITIALLY THOUGHT.

12:51.870 --> 12:53.861
THIS COULD BE
EXACTLY THE OPPOSITE.

12:53.900 --> 12:56.391
YEAH, LOOK, THERE ARE
PLACEMENT ERRORS
AND HESITATION MARKS.

12:56.440 --> 12:58.169
WHICH TELLS ME
HE'S IMPROVISING.

12:58.210 --> 13:00.428
HE'S STRUGGLING
THROUGH THE KILL AS IF
IT'S HIS FIRST TIME.

13:00.480 --> 13:02.072
WHAT IF IT IS?
WE COULD BE DEALING
WITH A KILLER

13:02.110 --> 13:03.202
WHO'S NOT YET
COMFORTABLE KILLING.

13:03.250 --> 13:05.047
THAT DOESN'T MAKE ANY SENSE.
BASED ON THE DISPOSAL SITES,

13:05.080 --> 13:07.048
WE PROFILED THIS GUY
HAD EXPERIENCE.

13:07.080 --> 13:09.378
YET THE ACTUAL MURDERS
TELL A FAR DIFFERENT STORY.

13:10.420 --> 13:13.218
[CELL PHONE RINGS]

13:13.260 --> 13:14.557
HEY.

13:14.590 --> 13:17.582
WHERE ARE YOU? ARE WE
STILL ON FOR DINNER?

13:17.630 --> 13:20.292
UH, WELL, I'M NOT SURE YET.

13:20.330 --> 13:23.390
I'M, UH--MIGHT BE
WORKING LATE AGAIN.

13:23.430 --> 13:24.920
IS EVERYTHING ALL RIGHT?

13:24.970 --> 13:26.835
YOU'VE BEEN WORKING LATE
THE PAST COUPLE OF NIGHTS.

13:26.870 --> 13:29.134
I'M FINE. JUST--

13:29.170 --> 13:33.231
TRYING TO FINISH UP
A PROJECT AT WORK.

13:33.280 --> 13:34.975
[SIGHS] RANDY, COME ON.

13:35.010 --> 13:36.409
WE JUST GOT ENGAGED.

13:36.440 --> 13:39.147
WE SHOULD BE ENJOYING
OURSELVES AND CELEBRATING.

13:39.180 --> 13:40.442
I KNOW. I KNOW.

13:40.480 --> 13:42.619
WHY DON'T YOU

13:42.650 --> 13:45.141
WRAP UP WHATEVER
YOU'RE DOING

13:45.190 --> 13:47.249
AND COME COME?

13:47.290 --> 13:49.451
OK.

13:49.490 --> 13:51.526
WELL, UH...

13:51.560 --> 13:54.324
I TOLD MOTHER I WOULD
STOP BY AFTER WORK.

13:54.360 --> 13:56.123
YOU CAN VISIT HER
TOMORROW.

13:56.160 --> 13:58.025
I'M SURE SHE'LL UNDERSTAND.

13:58.070 --> 13:59.526
YOU'RE RIGHT.

13:59.570 --> 14:01.094
I JUST NEED TO WRAP UP
A FEW THINGS.

14:01.140 --> 14:02.095
I'LL BE HOME.

14:02.140 --> 14:04.108
LOVE YOU. BYE.

14:04.140 --> 14:05.437
[KISS]

14:12.210 --> 14:14.212
OH! GOD, YOU SCARED ME.

14:14.250 --> 14:16.138
SORRY.

14:16.180 --> 14:17.647
UNFORTUNATELY,
OPEN HOUSE IS OVER.

14:17.690 --> 14:19.510
WELL, I WAS JUST HOPING
TO TAKE A QUICK PEEK.

14:19.550 --> 14:22.018
MY FIANCEE AND I
ARE LOOKING TO BUY SOON.

14:23.490 --> 14:24.525
SURE.

14:24.560 --> 14:25.982
I HAVE A FEW MINUTES.

14:26.030 --> 14:27.395
THAT'S ALL I NEED.

14:31.970 --> 14:35.064
OK, LOOK, THE OWNERS
PLACED THE HOUSE
ON THE MARKET,

14:35.100 --> 14:37.432
SO, IF YOU THINK...

14:40.940 --> 14:43.204
I DON'T GET IT.
HOW COULD THIS GUY
BE ORGANIZED

14:43.250 --> 14:45.206
AND DISORGANIZED
AT THE SAME TIME?

14:45.250 --> 14:46.911
THESE ARE TWO COMPLETELY
SPLIT M.O.s.

14:46.950 --> 14:49.248
WE HAVE TO CONSIDER
THE UNSUB MIGHT HAVE
A PARTNER.

14:49.280 --> 14:50.918
THAT MEANS
HE'S A SILENT PARTNER.

14:50.950 --> 14:53.350
BOTH DISPOSAL SITES
ONLY SHOWED EVIDENCE
OF ONE PERSON.

14:53.390 --> 14:54.914
CHANCES ARE IF THERE
WAS A PARTNER,

14:54.960 --> 14:57.053
HE'D SOMEHOW WANT TO
PARTICIPATE IN THE KILL.

14:57.090 --> 14:59.251
IT'S A WEIRD DICHOTOMY,
TYPICALLY SEEN
WHEN AN UNSUB

14:59.290 --> 15:01.258
IS IN THEIR EARLY STAGES
OF BECOMING A KILLER.

15:01.300 --> 15:04.064
EARLY STAGES. AS IN
YOU THINK THE MURDERER
COULD BE A KID.

15:04.100 --> 15:06.694
NO, I THINK HE'S LIVED
WITH THE FANTASY
FOR QUITE SOME TIME,

15:06.730 --> 15:08.368
BUT IT'S ONLY NOW
THAT HE'S FINALLY
ACTING ON IT.

15:08.400 --> 15:10.004
ONLY THINGS DON'T GO
AS PLANNED,

15:10.040 --> 15:11.234
SO HE STRUGGLES THROUGH
THE MURDER

15:11.270 --> 15:12.601
TRYING TO MATCH
THE ACTUAL KILL

15:12.640 --> 15:14.301
TO HIS LONG-GESTATING
FANTASY.

15:14.340 --> 15:16.535
AND IT'S ONLY
A MATTER OF TIME
BEFORE HIS HESITATION

15:16.580 --> 15:19.674
IN THE ACTUAL MURDER
CATCHES UP WITH
HIS STAGING FANTASY.

15:48.740 --> 15:54.349
[MUFFLED CRIES]

16:39.190 --> 16:41.351
VICTIM'S NAME
IS LINDA CALVARY.

16:41.400 --> 16:44.563
WORKED AS A REALTOR
BASED OUT OF DOWNTOWN.

16:44.600 --> 16:47.194
JANITOR DISCOVERED THE BODY
AND ALERTED POLICE.

16:47.240 --> 16:49.538
THE UNSUB DIDN'T TAKE HER
TO A SECONDARY LOCATION
TO KILL HER.

16:49.570 --> 16:51.060
DID IT RIGHT HERE.

16:51.110 --> 16:53.169
AND HE PLACED HER
IN A STALL.

16:53.210 --> 16:54.029
MAYBE HE WANTED
MORE PRIVACY THIS TIME.

16:54.080 --> 16:55.604
DIDN'T BOTHER USING
A BURLAP BAG EITHER.

16:55.640 --> 16:58.541
HE NO LONGER NEEDS A BARRIER
BETWEEN HIM AND HIS VICTIMS.

16:58.580 --> 17:01.310
NO HESITATION MARKS.

17:01.350 --> 17:02.442
WHY CHANGE HIS M.O. NOW?

17:02.480 --> 17:05.779
WELL, IT'S LIKE WE PROFILED.
HE'S GETTING MORE CONFIDENT.

17:05.820 --> 17:07.515
HE MIGHT BE GETTING CLOSER
TO HIS IDEAL TARGET.

17:07.560 --> 17:08.549
[CELL PHONE RINGS]

17:08.590 --> 17:10.182
HEY, WHAT UP, MAMA?

17:10.230 --> 17:12.482
I WAS ABLE TO NARROW
MY SEARCH DOWN
TO 5 TRUCKING COMPANIES,

17:12.530 --> 17:14.657
BUT THEY ALL CHECKED OUT.
NONE OF THEM HAVE TRUCKS
IN TRANSIT

17:14.700 --> 17:16.429
ON THOSE PARTICULAR ROUTES.

17:16.460 --> 17:17.825
THE TRUCK STOPS AREN'T
IMPORTANT TO HIM

17:17.870 --> 17:19.189
'CAUSE HE'S NOT A TRUCKER.

17:19.230 --> 17:20.333
THEY'RE IMPORTANT TO HIM
FOR ANOTHER REASON.

17:20.370 --> 17:23.237
WITH THE KNOWLEDGE THIS GUY
HAS OF ROUTES AND PATTERNS,

17:23.270 --> 17:25.602
HE'S GOTTA BE
CONNECTED TO SOMEONE
IN THE TRUCKING INDUSTRY.

17:25.640 --> 17:27.369
Garcia: WHOA.

17:27.410 --> 17:28.502
Lewis: WHAT IS IT,
GARCIA?

17:28.540 --> 17:31.475
I JUST FOUND SOME
SOMETHIN'-SOMETHIN'
ON FRANK MYERS,

17:31.510 --> 17:32.602
BEFORE HE WAS HOMELESS,

17:32.650 --> 17:35.642
HE WORKED IN FAMILY COURT
SERVICES AS A PUBLIC DEFENDER

17:35.680 --> 17:37.682
IN HARRINGTON COUNTY.

17:37.720 --> 17:38.687
[BEEP]

17:38.720 --> 17:40.278
AND--AND--AND THERE'S MORE.

17:40.320 --> 17:42.185
OUR THIRD VICTIM,
LINDA CALVARY,

17:42.220 --> 17:44.222
SHE JUST GOT HER
REAL ESTATE LICENSE
A FEW MONTHS AGO.

17:44.260 --> 17:45.557
BEFORE THEN, SHE WORKED
SHE WORKED AS A NURSE

17:45.590 --> 17:48.491
AND SHE TESTIFIED
IN A NUMBER OF THE SAME
CASES THAT FRANK WORKED.

17:48.530 --> 17:51.260
TWO OUT OF 3 OF THE VICTIMS
WORKED IN THE COURT SYSTEM.

17:51.300 --> 17:52.665
THESE VICTIMS WEREN'T
RANDOM. THEY WERE TARGETED.

17:52.700 --> 17:55.430
AND THE UNSUB IS WORKING
OFF OF A KILL LIST.

17:55.470 --> 17:57.665
IT'S TIME TO GIVE
THE PROFILE.

17:59.340 --> 18:01.137
AND THEN WHEN
IT'S ALL COMBINED,

18:01.180 --> 18:03.569
YOU SLOWLY ADD IN
3 LARGE EGGS,

18:03.610 --> 18:05.271
JUST ONE AT A TIME...

18:05.310 --> 18:09.269
Randy: THERE YOU ARE.
I'VE BEEN LOOKING
ALL OVER FOR YOU.

18:09.320 --> 18:12.187
YOU'RE NOT IN
YOUR USUAL SPOT.

18:12.220 --> 18:14.609
I BROUGHT YOU THESE.

18:14.660 --> 18:16.878
ONE CUP OF FLOUR.

18:16.920 --> 18:19.627
HALF A CUP OF
GROUND MACADAMIA NUTS.

18:19.660 --> 18:21.127
A TEASPOON OF...

18:21.160 --> 18:22.696
WHAT'S WRONG?
EVERYTHING OK?

18:22.730 --> 18:25.619
WHERE WERE YOU LAST NIGHT?
I WAITED FOR YOU.

18:25.670 --> 18:28.537
I'M SORRY. CHLOE
WANTED TO GET DINNER

18:28.570 --> 18:30.299
AND TALK ABOUT
WEDDING STUFF.

18:30.340 --> 18:32.365
HMM. WEDDING STUFF.

18:32.410 --> 18:34.207
YOU TWO JUST GOT ENGAGED.

18:34.240 --> 18:36.435
WELL, SHE'S EXCITED
TO START PLANNING.

18:36.480 --> 18:38.448
I KNOW WHERE
THIS IS GOING.

18:38.480 --> 18:40.209
WHAT ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

18:40.250 --> 18:43.242
THAT WOMAN WANTS
TO MONOPOLIZE
ALL OF YOUR TIME.

18:43.290 --> 18:45.884
MOTHER...

18:45.920 --> 18:47.683
NO NEED TO LIE TO ME.

18:47.720 --> 18:49.608
SHE'S JEALOUS.

18:49.660 --> 18:54.688
CHLOE JUST WANTS TO BE
THE ONLY WOMAN IN YOUR LIFE.

18:54.730 --> 18:57.164
THAT'S--THAT'S NOT TRUE.

18:57.200 --> 18:58.690
I CAN'T RESPECT ANY WOMAN

18:58.730 --> 19:02.461
WHO TRIES TO COME BETWEEN
A MOTHER AND HER CHILD.

19:02.500 --> 19:04.832
MOTHER, I WOULD NEVER
LET THAT HAPPEN.

19:06.510 --> 19:09.206
SHE'S JUST LIKE THE OTHERS
WHO TORE US APART.

19:09.240 --> 19:11.743
MOTHER, STOP.

19:11.780 --> 19:15.819
CHLOE IS NOT
THE GIRL FOR YOU.

19:15.850 --> 19:18.182
YOU CAN LEAVE NOW.

19:38.870 --> 19:40.428
WE BELIEVE THE UNSUB
WE'RE LOOKING FOR

19:40.480 --> 19:41.731
IS WHAT HE CALL
A RECTIFICATION KILLER.

19:41.780 --> 19:43.839
HE'S TARGETING PEOPLE
THAT HE HOLDS RESPONSIBLE

19:43.880 --> 19:45.848
FOR A MAJOR TRAUMA
IN HIS CHILDHOOD.

19:45.880 --> 19:48.678
THESE FEELINGS HAVE BEEN
FESTERING IN HIS MIND
FOR DECADES,

19:48.720 --> 19:49.914
AS EVIDENCED
BY THE DEGREE OF RAGE.

19:49.950 --> 19:51.781
Lewis: BECAUSE OF THE
COMPLEXITY OF THESE CRIMES

19:51.820 --> 19:52.980
AND THEIR VICTIMOLOGY,

19:53.020 --> 19:56.285
WE BELIEVE THIS PERSON
TO BE A WHITE MALE
IN HIS 305 OR 405.

19:56.320 --> 19:58.982
JJ: THE VICTIMS ACTUALLY
INTERACTED WITH THE UNSUB
AS A CHILD

19:59.030 --> 20:00.895
WHEN THEY WORKED
IN THE FAMILY COURT SYSTEM.

20:00.930 --> 20:04.366
Rossi: IT'S POSSIBLE HE
WAS REMOVED FROM HIS FAMILY
FOR HIS OWN SAFETY

20:04.400 --> 20:05.867
BUT WAS TOO YOUNG
A THE TIME

20:05.900 --> 20:07.959
TO KNOW THE SEVERITY
OF THE SITUATION.

20:08.000 --> 20:10.434
Reid: NOW THAT HE'S AN ADULT,
HE THINKS IT'S HIS MISSION

20:10.470 --> 20:11.801
SO SEEK REVENGE ON THOSE
IN THE LEGAL SYSTEM

20:11.840 --> 20:15.503
HE BELIEVES BROKE UP
HIS FAMILY.

20:15.540 --> 20:17.599
HotCh: IT'S POSSIBLE
THE TRIGGERING EVENT

20:17.650 --> 20:20.949
WAS THE SEPARATION
OR DEATH OF ONE OR BOTH
OF HIS PARENTS.

20:20.980 --> 20:22.845
Rossi: CHECK FOR RULINGS
INVOLVING A CHILD

20:22.880 --> 20:25.986
BEING PLACED INTO
THE FOSTER CARE SYSTEM
OR PUT UP FOR ADOPTION.

20:26.020 --> 20:28.511
THIS GUY'S EXHIBITING
AN IRRESISTIBLE COMPULSION

20:28.560 --> 20:30.858
BY POSING HIS VICTIMS
AT TRUCK STOP REST ROOMS,

20:30.890 --> 20:32.619
DESPITE THE ESCALATING
RISKS.

20:32.660 --> 20:34.855
AND THIS INDICATES
THAT HIS CHILDHOOD TRAUMA

20:34.900 --> 20:37.494
MAY HAVE SOME DIRECT LINK
TO THESE TYPE OF LOCATIONS.

20:37.530 --> 20:40.397
FOCUS ON CASES THAT INVOLVE
A PARENT OR GUARDIAN

20:40.440 --> 20:41.737
CONNECTED TO
THE TRUCKING INDUSTRY

20:41.770 --> 20:43.408
OR WHO HAVE SPENT
LONG PERIODS OF TIME

20:43.440 --> 20:44.998
TRAVELING ON THE OPEN ROAD.

20:45.040 --> 20:47.634
WE BELIEVE THAT LOCATING
THIS CASE WILL BE THE KEY
TO FINDING HIM.

20:47.680 --> 20:49.602
THANK YOU.

21:22.840 --> 21:25.547
Man: NO! NO!

21:25.580 --> 21:28.913
[GROANING]

21:31.350 --> 21:36.458
NO! [CRYING OUT,
GROANING]

21:38.030 --> 21:39.884
AAH . ..
RAN DY, WAKE UP.

21:39.930 --> 21:42.922
[GASPS,
BREATHING HARD]

21:44.630 --> 21:45.961
I DIDN'T HEAR YOU
COME IN.

21:46.000 --> 21:48.093
YOU HAVEN'T BEEN
TAKING YOUR MEDS?

21:48.140 --> 21:49.232
I CALLED THE PHARMACIST.

21:49.270 --> 21:51.909
HE SAID YOU HAVEN'T REFILLED
YOUR PRESCRIPTION IN MONTHS.

21:51.940 --> 21:53.009
I KNOW.

21:53.040 --> 21:54.337
WHAT ARE YOU THINKING?

21:54.380 --> 21:55.870
THEY WEREN'T WORKING.

21:55.910 --> 21:57.844
THEY'RE THE ONLY THING
THAT WORKS.

21:57.880 --> 21:59.040
CHLOE, PLEASE STOP.

21:59.080 --> 22:02.709
THAT'S WHY YOU'VE BEEN HAVING
THOSE DREAMS AGAIN, ISN'T IT?

22:02.750 --> 22:04.911
MOTHER THOUGHT IT
WOULD BE BEST IF MAYBE
I STOPPED TAKING--

22:04.950 --> 22:07.453
WAIT. SHE TOLD YOU
TO STOP TAKING YOUR PILLS?

22:07.490 --> 22:09.082
AND YOU LISTENED?

22:09.120 --> 22:10.929
OF COURSE I LISTENED.

22:10.960 --> 22:12.621
SHE'S MY MOTHER.

22:12.660 --> 22:14.958
YOU'VE ONLY KNOWN HER
FOR A COUPLE OF MONTHS.

22:15.000 --> 22:17.992
IT'S NOT HER PLACE, RANDY.

22:18.030 --> 22:20.089
FIRST IT'S YOUR MEDS
AND THEN IT'S YOUR TIME.

22:20.130 --> 22:24.999
YOU'RE NOT OBLIGATED
TO SPEND EVERY WAKING
MOMENT WITH HER.

22:25.040 --> 22:26.837
CAN'T YOU SEE
SHE'S HURTING YOU?

22:26.870 --> 22:27.939
I SAID STOP!

22:27.980 --> 22:29.004
[LAMP SHATTERS]

22:29.040 --> 22:30.678
RANDY, WHAT'S WRONG WITH YOU?

22:30.710 --> 22:32.803
THIS IS THE SAME WOMAN
THAT ABANDONED YOU.

22:32.850 --> 22:35.978
SHE DID NOT ABANDON ME.

22:36.020 --> 22:38.841
[GASPING] AH! UHH!

22:38.890 --> 22:42.053
I'M STARTING TO THINK
MAYBE MOTHER WAS RIGHT
ABOUT YOU.

22:42.090 --> 22:44.058
[GASPS]

22:50.600 --> 22:52.989
WE KNOW HOW THE SECOND
AND THIRD VICTIM
ARE CONNECTED,

22:53.030 --> 22:56.067
BUT HOW DOES
CLAIRE WESTCHESTER
FIT INTO THE PUZZLE?

22:56.100 --> 22:57.192
WELL, LET'S GO THROUGH IT AGAIN.
WHAT DO WE KNOW ABOUT HER?

22:57.240 --> 22:58.559
Morgan: SHE WAS
A SCHOOLTEACHER
FOR CLOSE TO 30 YEARS.

22:58.610 --> 23:01.704
Rossi: NEVER HAD KIDS,
BUT LOVED HER STUDENTS
LIKE THEY WERE HER OWN.

23:01.740 --> 23:03.549
SHE WAS EXTREMELY HANDS-ON,

23:03.580 --> 23:07.004
ESPECIALLY TO THOSE CHILDREN
WHO SHE FELT WERE IN NEED.

23:07.050 --> 23:08.711
KIDS.

23:08.750 --> 23:10.718
KIDS. WAIT A MINUTE.

23:10.750 --> 23:13.048
IF THE UNSUB IS WORKING
OFF A KILL LIST,

23:13.090 --> 23:16.014
IT'S POSSIBLE HE WAS ONE OF
CLAIRE'S FORMER STUDENTS.

23:16.060 --> 23:17.550
THAT COULD BE OUR CONNECTION.

23:17.590 --> 23:19.729
THAT MAKES SENSE.
IF THERE WAS SOMETHING
OFF AT HOME,

23:19.760 --> 23:20.852
SHE WOULD NOTICE
SIGNS OF ABUSE

23:20.900 --> 23:22.549
AND REPORT IT
TO THE AUTHORITIES.

23:22.600 --> 23:23.692
SHE COULD HAVE BEEN
THE CATALYST

23:23.730 --> 23:25.129
FOR GETTING HIM REMOVED
FROM HIS HOME.

23:25.170 --> 23:26.762
BUT BASED ON OUR PROFILE,

23:26.800 --> 23:27.892
HE WOULD HAVE BEEN
TOO YOUNG

23:27.940 --> 23:29.896
TO HAVE KNOWN
THE NAMES OF EVERYONE.

23:29.940 --> 23:31.237
NOT TO MENTION CASE FILES
WEREN'T DIGITAL.

23:31.270 --> 23:34.433
HE WOULDN'T HAVE BEEN ABLE
TO GAIN ACCESS TO THAT
INFORMATION TODAY.

23:34.480 --> 23:36.175
SO HOW DOES THIS GUY
KNOW WHO TO TARGET?

23:36.210 --> 23:38.075
MAYBE THE NAMES
WERE FED TO HIM.

23:38.110 --> 23:40.078
WE PROFILED EARLIER THE
POSSIBILITY OF A PARTNER.

23:40.110 --> 23:41.748
THERE COULD BE SOMETHING
TO THAT.

23:41.780 --> 23:43.441
IF THAT'S THE CASE,
THAT PERSON
WOULD NEED TO FEEL

23:43.490 --> 23:46.084
AS WRONGED BY THE VICTIMS
AS THE UNSUB HIMSELF.

23:46.120 --> 23:47.951
GREEN FOR GO.
A PARENT.

23:47.990 --> 23:50.083
GARCIA, WE THINK
THAT THE UNSUB MAY BE
WORKING WITH A PARTNER,

23:50.120 --> 23:51.724
A PARENT OR GUARDIAN.

23:51.760 --> 23:53.591
AND, BABY GIRL,
CHECK SCHOOL RECORDS

23:53.630 --> 23:55.598
FOR MALE STUDENTS WHO WERE
IN CLAIRE WESTCHESTER'S CLASS

23:56.800 --> 23:57.926
YEAH. KEEP TALKING.

23:57.970 --> 24:00.029
IT'S POSSIBLE CLAIRE
FILED A COMPLAINT

24:00.070 --> 24:01.628
WITH THE SCHOOL
AGAINST THE PARENT,

24:01.670 --> 24:03.865
WHICH RESULTED IN
THE UNSUB BEING REMOVED
FROM HIS HOME.

24:03.910 --> 24:05.537
AND CROSS-CHECK THAT
WITH HOSPITAL RECORDS.

24:05.570 --> 24:07.504
HE MIGHT HAVE MADE
FREQUENT TRIPS TO THE E.R.

24:07.540 --> 24:10.998
JUST AS RANDY MARTIN
AGED OUT OF THE SYSTEM,

24:11.050 --> 24:13.518
RANDY JACOBS POPPED UP.
BUT AS FAR AS I CAN TELL,

24:13.550 --> 24:16.917
HE HAS NO CRIMINAL HISTORY.
HE HAS A STABLE JOB.

24:16.950 --> 24:20.784
AND HE RECENTLY GOT ENGAGED
TO HIS LONG-TIME GIRLFRIEND
CHLOE ANDREWS.

24:20.820 --> 24:25.154
SOUNDS LIKE HE WENT FROM
A MODEL CITIZEN
TO A COLD-BLOODED MURDERER.

24:25.190 --> 24:28.853
HIS BIRTHMOTHER FLORA MARTIN
HAS QUITE A HISTORY, HOWEVER.

24:28.900 --> 24:30.151
CHECK YOUR TABLETS.

24:30.200 --> 24:32.964
[TABLETS BEEPING]

24:35.040 --> 24:38.532
WELL, AROUND THE TIME
RANDY WOULD HAVE BEEN
CONCEIVED,

24:38.570 --> 24:40.208
FLORA WAS ADMITTED
TO THE HOSPITAL.
SHE'D BEEN RAPED.

24:40.240 --> 24:41.878
SHE WAS 30 AT THE TIME.

24:41.910 --> 24:43.741
I SAYS HERE SHE'D BEEN
HITCHHIKING

24:43.780 --> 24:45.873
AND WAS SEXUALLY ASSAULTED
BY A TRUCK DRIVER.

24:45.910 --> 24:47.719
ACCORDING TO HER STATEMENT,
HER ATTACKER DRAGGED HER

24:47.750 --> 24:50.639
INTO A TRUCK STOP REST ROOM
AND DID BAD THINGS.

24:50.690 --> 24:52.942
THAT'S THE EXACT SAME. M.O.
THAT CAN'T BE A COINCIDENCE.

24:52.990 --> 24:54.855
THIS CASE IS THE NEXUS.

24:54.890 --> 24:56.778
SO MOTHER AND SON
MUST HAVE RECENTLY REUNITED

24:56.820 --> 24:59.027
AND HE'S BEEN GOING
OFF THE KILL LIST
THAT SHE PROVIDED.

24:59.060 --> 25:01.995
GARCIA, WHAT ELSE DO WE KNOW
ABOUT FLORA MARTIN?

25:02.030 --> 25:06.729
9 MONTHS AFTER HER ALLEGED RAPE
SHE GAVE BIRTH TO A SON.

25:06.770 --> 25:09.989
THERE WAS NO FATHER LISTED
ON THE BIRTH CERTIFICATE.

25:10.040 --> 25:10.961
[BEEP]

25:11.010 --> 25:13.160
Morgan: SO HER SON IS
A PRODUCT OF THAT RAPE.

25:13.210 --> 25:16.668
HotCh: WHERE IS SHE NOW?

25:16.710 --> 25:18.575
SHE IS...

25:20.580 --> 25:23.617
IN A PRISON INSANE ASYLUM

25:23.650 --> 25:25.083
FOR THE MURDER
OF 6 TRUCKERS.

25:28.120 --> 25:30.588
NAME OF THE PATIENT
YOU'RE HERE TO SEE?

25:30.630 --> 25:32.086
FLORA MARTIN.

25:33.660 --> 25:36.754
[DOOR BUZZES OPEN]

25:52.650 --> 25:55.471
I'M SORRY ABOUT
LAST NIGHT, MOTHER.

25:59.350 --> 26:01.784
I WANT TO SHOW YOU
SOMETHING.

26:01.820 --> 26:04.050
WHAT IS IT?

26:04.090 --> 26:06.126
YOU'LL SEE.

26:20.070 --> 26:21.833
WHAT DO YOU THINK?

26:25.250 --> 26:28.811
HONEY, IT'S PERFECT.

26:38.430 --> 26:41.092
Randy: I'LL NEVER MISS
ANOTHER VISIT, I PROMISE.

26:41.130 --> 26:43.098
Flora: IT'S OK, HONEY.

26:43.130 --> 26:45.098
EVEN WHEN YOU MAKE MISTAKES,

26:45.130 --> 26:49.066
I AM ALWAYS GOING
TO LOVE YOU.

26:49.100 --> 26:52.934
[SIGHS] ALL THE HARD WORK
YOU DID.

26:52.970 --> 26:59.409
AND IT IS EVEN BETTER
THAN I COULD HAVE IMAGINED.

26:59.450 --> 27:02.214
YOU REALLY LIKE IT?

27:02.250 --> 27:04.980
OHH, OF COURSE I DO.

27:05.020 --> 27:09.150
I MEAN, WHAT MORE
COULD A MOTHER ASK FOR?

27:09.190 --> 27:11.181
OHH...

27:11.230 --> 27:13.152
[CRYING]

27:16.200 --> 27:18.259
HONEY, WHAT'S BOTHERING YOU?

27:20.130 --> 27:22.997
YOU WERE RIGHT ABOUT CHLOE.

27:23.040 --> 27:24.928
I DON'T KNOW WHY
I DIDN'T SEE IT.

27:24.970 --> 27:27.404
SHE WANTS TO TEAR US
APART.

27:27.440 --> 27:29.704
IT IS NOT YOUR FAULT.

27:29.740 --> 27:32.004
THAT WOMAN IS MANIPULATIVE.

27:32.050 --> 27:37.044
WHY, YOU WERE JUST BLINDED
BY WHAT YOU THOUGHT WAS LOVE.

27:38.420 --> 27:42.117
NOW YOU HAVE TO COMPLETELY
FREE YOURSELF.

27:42.160 --> 27:44.879
HOW?

27:44.930 --> 27:49.094
ISN'T IT OBVIOUS?

27:49.130 --> 27:51.360
YOU HAVE TO KILL HER.

27:53.300 --> 27:56.895
IT'LL MAKE EVERYTHING BETTER.

27:56.940 --> 27:58.908
Lewis: SO THE KILLER
IN RANDY WAS DORMANT

27:58.940 --> 28:00.407
UNTIL HE RECONNECTED
WITH HIS MOTHER.

28:00.440 --> 28:02.408
Morgan: YOU ADD THAT TO
FLORA'S TWISTED VERSION
OF THE STORY,

28:02.440 --> 28:03.941
THERE'S YOUR TRIGGER.

28:03.980 --> 28:05.277
YEAH, FLORA'S GOING AFTER
THE PEOPLE

28:05.310 --> 28:07.369
SHE HOLDS RESPONSIBLE
FOR TAKING RANDY AWAY FROM HER.

28:07.410 --> 28:09.878
IT EXPLAINS THE DICHOTOMY.

28:09.920 --> 28:13.139
RANDY COMMITTED THE MURDERS
BASED ON THE BLUEPRINT
HIS MOTHER PROVIDED.

28:13.190 --> 28:15.158
YEAH. AND AT THIS POINT
WE'VE GOT A FULL-FLEDGED
KILLER ON OUR HANDS.

28:15.190 --> 28:17.454
ONCE HE'S DONE WITH
THAT LIST OF NAMES,
WHAT HAPPENS NEXT?

28:17.490 --> 28:19.253
WELL, HE'LL EITHER
START KILLING ON HIS OWN

28:19.290 --> 28:21.190
OR FLORA WILL CONTINUE
TO MANIPULATE HIM

28:21.230 --> 28:23.448
INTO CARRYING OUT
HER OWN VENGEANCE.

28:23.500 --> 28:27.322
HIS MOTHER CONVINCED HIM
TO GET OFF HIS MEDS.

28:27.370 --> 28:29.497
I KNOW, BUT...

28:29.540 --> 28:31.508
FIRST I NEED TO GET
OUT OF HERE.

28:31.540 --> 28:33.735
I JUST NEED
TO GRAB MY KEYS.

28:35.040 --> 28:37.941
OH, GOD. I THINK HE'S BACK.

28:37.980 --> 28:40.448
STAY ON THE PHONE WITH ME.

29:03.870 --> 29:05.531
I'M FINE.

29:05.570 --> 29:09.108
I'M LITERALLY
WALKING OUT NOW.

29:09.140 --> 29:10.471
SEE YOU IN A FEW.

29:45.510 --> 29:47.478
Lewis: FLORA MARTIN?
Guard: RIGHT THERE.

29:47.510 --> 29:50.513
OH. I WASN'T EXPECTING
VISITORS.

29:50.550 --> 29:52.381
WELL, WE'RE FROM THE FBI.

29:52.420 --> 29:54.012
I'M AGENT LEWIS.
THIS IS AGENT MORGAN.

29:54.060 --> 29:56.551
I SEE. TO WHAT
DO I OWE THIS HONOR?

29:56.590 --> 29:58.581
WE'RE HERE TO TALK TO YOU
ABOUT YOUR SON RANDY.

29:58.630 --> 30:00.928
WE BELIEVE HE'S BEEN
INVOLVED IN AT LEAST
3 MURDERS.

30:00.960 --> 30:03.155
WOULD YOU KNOW
ANYTHING ABOUT THAT?

30:03.200 --> 30:06.192
WELL, I'VE BEEN LOCKED UP HERE
FOR THE LAST 24 YEARS.

30:06.230 --> 30:08.369
I'M THE LAST PERSON
YOU SHOULD BE ASKING.

30:08.400 --> 30:11.528
MS. MARTIN, RECORDS SHOW
THAT YOUR SON HAS BEEN
VISITING YOU EVERY DAY

30:11.570 --> 30:12.400
FOR THE PAST 3 MONTHS.

30:12.440 --> 30:14.579
WE THINK YOU KNOW
QUITE A BIT ABOUT IT.

30:14.610 --> 30:17.431
Lewis: IN FACT,
YOU KNOW WHAT I THINK?

30:17.480 --> 30:20.574
I THINK YOU KNOW EXACTLY
WHAT YOUR SON'S BEEN UP TO,

30:20.610 --> 30:24.580
AND YOU'RE ABSOLUTELY
THRILLED THAT HE PICKED UP
WHERE YOU LEFT OFF.

30:24.620 --> 30:27.282
Rossi: RANDY JACOBS,
THIS IS THE FBI!

30:30.660 --> 30:32.582
CLEAR!

30:32.630 --> 30:34.427
CLEAR!

30:34.460 --> 30:36.496
DEFINITELY SIGNS
OF A STRUGGLE.

30:36.530 --> 30:38.964
RANDY CAN NO LONGER
CONTAIN HIS RAGE.

30:39.000 --> 30:40.092
HE'S UNRAVELING.

30:40.130 --> 30:41.529
BY THE LOOKS OF IT,

30:41.570 --> 30:44.368
HE MAY ALREADY HAVE
HIS NEXT VICTIM.

30:44.410 --> 30:46.605
ALL RIGHT,
THAN KS, ROSSI.

30:46.640 --> 30:49.108
BOTH RANDY
AND HIS FIANCEE
CHLOE ARE MISSING.

30:49.140 --> 30:50.903
HOTCH JUST ISSUED
AN APB.

30:50.950 --> 30:54.909
HMM. FLORA MAY HAVE
CONVINCED RANDY
THAT CHLOE WAS A THREAT.

30:54.950 --> 30:56.508
WE'RE RUNNING
OUT OF TIME.

30:56.550 --> 30:59.110
HEY, YOU KNOW WHAT?
I THINK SHE MIGHT BE
MORE FORTHCOMING

30:59.150 --> 31:01.914
IF IT WAS JUST THE TWO OF US.

31:03.560 --> 31:06.358
THANKS.
I'LL BE RIGHT OUTSIDE.

31:09.960 --> 31:12.622
DO YOU HAVE
ANY CHILDREN, AGENT?

31:12.670 --> 31:14.558
I DON'T.

31:14.600 --> 31:18.366
BUT I CAN IMAGINE
HOW REWARDING IT MUST BE
TO BE A PARENT,

31:18.410 --> 31:22.232
SEE YOUR CHILD GROW UP
AND BECOME SUCCESSFUL.

31:22.280 --> 31:24.009
I ALSO KNOW
THAT A LOT OF PARENTS

31:24.050 --> 31:26.644
TRY TO LIVE VICARIOUSLY
THROUGH THEIR CHILDREN.

31:26.680 --> 31:29.979
BUT FOR SOMEBODY LIKE YOU...

31:30.020 --> 31:32.648
IT'S ABOUT MORE
THAN JUST REVENGE.

31:32.690 --> 31:36.012
FOR YOU, EVERY MURDER
THAT RANDY COMMITS

31:36.060 --> 31:38.358
ALLOWS YOU TO RELIVE
YOUR OWN CRIMES,

31:38.390 --> 31:40.529
OVER AND OVER AGAIN,

31:40.560 --> 31:42.619
DOWN TO THE LAST DETAIL.

31:42.660 --> 31:44.298
IS THAT RIGHT?

31:44.330 --> 31:48.039
THERE IS SO MUCH ANGER
INSIDE OF YOU

31:48.070 --> 31:51.164
THAT YOU WOULD DESTROY
YOUR OWN SON'S LIFE.

31:51.210 --> 31:53.701
I KNOW WHAT HAPPENED
TO YOU 30 YEARS AGO.

31:53.740 --> 31:56.607
I KNOW WHAT THAT MAN
DID TO YOU.

32:02.150 --> 32:05.984
PLEASE. PLEASE,
DON'T DO THIS.

32:06.020 --> 32:06.987
SHH, SHH, SHH.

32:07.020 --> 32:10.080
WE ARE GONNA HAVE
SOME FUN.

32:10.120 --> 32:12.953
[SOBBING]

32:18.770 --> 32:19.896
FLORA.

32:23.770 --> 32:25.635
[CRYING]

32:25.670 --> 32:28.138
I WILL NEVER FORGET
HIS FACE.

32:30.210 --> 32:34.112
OR HIS HANDS ON MY SKIN
OR THE SMELL OF HIS BREATH.

32:41.560 --> 32:45.348
[SCREAMING]

32:49.700 --> 32:54.433
HE SAID EVERY TIME
I LOOK IN A MIRROR...

32:57.070 --> 33:01.006
I WOULD...REMEMBER HIM.

33:02.710 --> 33:05.099
HE'S THE REASON
YOU STARTED KILLING.

33:05.150 --> 33:07.004
OHH...

33:07.050 --> 33:10.110
FLORA, YOU KILLED
6 TRUCKERS.

33:10.150 --> 33:11.549
WHY NOT MORE?

33:11.590 --> 33:14.354
I GOT CAUGHT.

33:14.390 --> 33:16.210
NO. NO.

33:16.260 --> 33:17.386
YOU ELUDED THE AUTHORITIES
FOR MONTHS

33:17.420 --> 33:19.229
BEFORE THEY FOUND YOU
HOLED UP IN THAT BARN

33:19.260 --> 33:20.625
OUTSIDE THE CITY.

33:20.660 --> 33:23.697
YOU COULD HAVE EASILY
KEPT KILLING,
BUT YOU STOPPED.

33:23.730 --> 33:25.561
IT WAS TIME TO GIVE UP.

33:25.600 --> 33:29.161
SEE, I DON'T THINK
YOU GAVE UP.

33:29.200 --> 33:30.462
I THINK YOU STOPPED

33:30.500 --> 33:33.162
BECAUSE YOU FOUND
WHO YOU WERE LOOKING FOR.

33:33.210 --> 33:36.031
THE MAN WHO RAPED YOU.

33:36.080 --> 33:39.447
RAN DY'S FATHER.

33:39.480 --> 33:41.744
HIS FATHER
IS OUT AT THAT BARN,

33:41.780 --> 33:43.213
ISN'T HE?

34:04.210 --> 34:08.135
MOTHER WAS RIGHT.

34:08.180 --> 34:11.672
THIS PLACE IS PERFECT.

34:22.190 --> 34:24.181
SOMEBODY HELP ME!

34:24.230 --> 34:26.528
OH! OH! AAH!

34:26.560 --> 34:28.494
NO, PLEASE!

34:28.530 --> 34:29.656
[CRYING]

34:29.700 --> 34:32.589
PLEASE, WE CAN TALK.

34:32.630 --> 34:36.236
YOU'RE NEVER GONNA
UNDERSTAND ME.

34:36.270 --> 34:40.707
[CRYING OUT]

35:07.330 --> 35:08.866
CHLOE, OPEN THE DOOR.

35:08.900 --> 35:10.697
LET ME IN!

35:16.710 --> 35:20.578
I DON'T WANT TO HURT YOU.

35:24.590 --> 35:27.218
I DON'T WANT TO HURT YOU.

35:30.260 --> 35:32.524
[SIRENS]

35:35.300 --> 35:36.653
CHLOE?
[GASPING]

35:36.700 --> 35:38.167
CHLOE, I'M COMING IN.

35:38.200 --> 35:40.589
PLEASE, RAN DY!

35:40.630 --> 35:42.393
YOU DON'T HAVE TO DO THIS.

35:42.440 --> 35:44.635
[SOBBING]

35:44.670 --> 35:47.264
[SIRENS]

36:10.700 --> 36:12.224
HELP! I'M IN HERE!

36:12.270 --> 36:14.238
OHH!

36:18.000 --> 36:19.934
RAN DY JACOBS, FBI.

36:21.410 --> 36:22.434
LET HER GO.

36:22.480 --> 36:23.572
STAY AWAY.

36:27.280 --> 36:29.919
STAY AWAY!

36:29.950 --> 36:32.282
DROP THE KNIFE, RANDY.

36:32.320 --> 36:34.254
PLEASE LISTEN TO THEM.

36:34.290 --> 36:36.815
DO YOU KNOW WHY
YOU BROUGHT CHLOE HERE?

36:39.530 --> 36:41.919
THIS PLACE MEANS
SOMETHING TO YOU.

36:41.960 --> 36:45.726
YOU'VE BEEN HERE BEFORE.

36:56.440 --> 36:59.739
Morgan: RANDY, YOUR
MOTHER'S BEEN USING YOU
SINCE YOU WERE A CHILD.

36:59.780 --> 37:01.839
THAT'S WHY YOU WERE
TAKEN AWAY FROM HER.

37:01.880 --> 37:03.677
Lewis:
YOU WERE HER PATSY.

37:03.720 --> 37:07.247
SHE NEEDED YOU TO CONTINUE
TO DO HER DIRTY WORK.

37:07.290 --> 37:10.509
SHE WAS USING YOU BACK THEN
AND SHE'S STILL USING YOU NOW.

37:57.870 --> 38:01.909
[WHIMPERING]

38:03.710 --> 38:05.371
AAH!

38:05.410 --> 38:07.742
Lewis: RANDY.

38:07.780 --> 38:09.771
YOUR MOTHER FORCED YOU
TO PARTICIPATE

38:09.820 --> 38:11.481
IN THE MURDER
OF YOUR FATHER.

38:16.360 --> 38:18.624
AND THEN THE TWO OF YOU
BURIED HIM HERE.

38:21.830 --> 38:23.957
Morgan: COME ON, MAN.

38:24.000 --> 38:26.525
WE ALL HAVE CHOICES.

38:27.670 --> 38:30.332
Lewis: IT'S NOT TOO LATE
FOR YOU TO CHOOSE

38:30.370 --> 38:32.759
TO DO THE RIGHT THING.

38:32.810 --> 38:34.732
YOU DO NOT HAVE TO BE
DEFINED

38:34.780 --> 38:37.408
BY THE SINS OF YOUR FATHER
OR YOUR MOTHER.

38:43.520 --> 38:45.112
[GASPING]

38:45.150 --> 38:47.345
COME HERE.

38:47.390 --> 38:49.654
ALL RIGHT. ALL RIGHT.

38:56.600 --> 38:59.592
I'M SO SORRY.

39:07.570 --> 39:09.435
Lewis: "THE INFLUENCE
OF A MOTHER

39:09.480 --> 39:11.038
"IN THE LIVES
OF HER CHILDREN

39:11.080 --> 39:13.571
IS BEYOND CALCULATION."

39:13.610 --> 39:15.441
JAMES E. FAUST.

39:15.480 --> 39:17.414
FLORA SIGNED A CONFESSION.

39:17.450 --> 39:18.917
SHE ADMITTED
TO MAKING RANDY

39:18.950 --> 39:20.588
PARTICIPATE
IN HIS FATHER'S MURDER.

39:20.620 --> 39:22.451
JJ: ALL THIS TIME
HE SEEMED TO HAVE

39:22.490 --> 39:25.459
SUCH A NORMAL,
WELL-ADJUSTED LIFE.

39:25.490 --> 39:27.549
YEAH, BUT THERE WAS ALWAYS
THAT VOID INSIDE OF HIM.

39:27.590 --> 39:29.820
EVEN AFTER HE FOUND OUT
WHO HIS MOTHER WAS,

39:29.860 --> 39:30.997
HE STILL WANTED TO BUILD
A RELATIONSHIP.

39:31.030 --> 39:33.624
YEAH. AND THAT'S HOW
SHE WAS ABLE TO PLAY
ON HIS EMOTIONS.

39:33.670 --> 39:37.731
AND HE WANTED RETRIBUTION
FOR HIS MOTHER,
NO MATTER THE COST.

39:37.770 --> 39:40.739
JJ: SOMETIMES WE LET
THE NEED TO CONNECT

39:40.770 --> 39:43.807
AND BOND WITH OUR
FAMILIES TRUMP ANY KIND
OF JUDGMENT.

39:43.840 --> 39:47.879
Lewis: AND THAT'S MORE POWERFUL
THAN ANYONE CAN UNDERSTAND.

39:47.910 --> 39:51.118
* A DANCE OF BREEZE

39:51.150 --> 39:55.086
* FROM HUSH-A-BYE MOUNTAIN

39:55.120 --> 40:02.094
* SOFTLY FLOW
O'ER LULLABY BAY *

40:02.130 --> 40:09.969
* IT FILLS THE SAILS
OF BOATS THAT ARE WAITING *

40:10.000 --> 40:18.169
* WAITING TO SAIL
YOUR WORRIES AWAY *

40:22.780 --> 40:31.017
* IT ISN'T FAR
TO HUSH-A-BYE MOUNTAIN *

40:31.060 --> 40:37.750
* AND YOUR BOAT
WAITS DOWN BY THE KEY *

40:37.800 --> 40:45.900
* THE WINDS OF NIGHT
SO SOFTLY ARE SIGHING *

40:45.940 --> 40:54.575
* SOON THEY WILL FLY
YOUR TROUBLES TO SEA *

40:54.620 --> 41:03.210
* SO CLOSE YOUR EYES
ON HUSH-A-BYE MOUNTAIN *

41:03.260 --> 41:10.553
* WAVE GOOD-BYE
TO CARES OF THE DAY *

41:10.600 --> 41:13.524
* AND WATCH YOUR BOAT

41:13.570 --> 41:17.631
* FROM HUSH-A-BYE MOUNTAIN
WE NEED AN AMBULANCE NOW!

41:17.670 --> 41:20.662
* SO FAR AWAY
FROM LULLABY BAY *
